  "short_text": "Validate Password",
  "content": "Write a program to check if the given string is a valid password or not. A string is considered as a valid password if the number of characters present is greater than 7.<hr><b>Input</b><br/><br/>The input will be a single line containing a word.<hr><b>Output</b><br/><br/>The output should be True or False.<hr><b>Explanation</b><br/><br/>For example, if the given input is &quot;passwd&quot;, it has only 6 characters (less than 7). So the output should be False.",
